 0833:     """
 0834:     Allows exporting a game as a string.
 0835: 
 0836:     >>> import chess.pgn
 0837:     >>>
 0838:     >>> game = chess.pgn.Game()
 0839:     >>>
 0840:     >>> exporter = chess.pgn.StringExporter(headers=True, variations=True, comments=True)
